      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">NORTHERN TERRITORY ¶ APPLICATION FOR LEASE OF PASTORAL LANDS, UNDER ACT 48, 1876. ¶ Term ¶  25  ¶ Years ¶  from 1st April 1878. ¶ Application No. ¶   ¶ 2798  ¶ of ¶ containing  ¶ 130  ¶ square miles £...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">78.01.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To the Surveyor General of South Australia</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">E1652/1/1878/2798, National Archives of Australia, Darwin.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Annotation: 'Copy f[or Adelaide]'.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">NORTHERN TERRITORY</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">APPLICATION FOR LEASE OF PASTORAL LANDS, UNDER ACT 48, 1876.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Term</seg> 25 <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Years</seg> from 1st April 1878.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">
                  <seg style="font-variant: small-caps; ">Application No.</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; "> </seg>2798 <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">of</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Spaces are left blank here and in several other places on the form.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">containing </seg>130 <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">square miles £</seg>3 <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">:</seg>5/ -<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Dated</seg> 30 Jany <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">18</seg>78.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I Ferdinand Jacob Heinrich Von Mueller <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">of</seg> Melbourne Victoria<seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; "> do hereby make application for a Lease of a certain portion of the Waste Lands of the Crown in the Northern Territory of South Australia, the situation and boundaries whereof are shown in the Plan hereto annexed, to which <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>have affixed <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>signature; and <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/> make the above claim under clause 4 of the Regulations now in force (dated 28th December, 1876).</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Clause 4 of the regulations specified the way in which an application was to be made and 'except in cases where the land applied for is partia</seg>
                     <seg style="">lly bounded by runs already leased, or where the natural feature of the country may render a regular outline impracticable, the land applied for shall be of rectangular form, the length of which shall not exceed twice its breadth, and one of the sides of which shall run as nearly as may be in a north and south direction'. Clause 2 of the regulations required the property to be stocked within three years 'at the rate of at least two head of great cattle [i.e., </seg>'all manner of beasts except sheep and yearlings' (<ref target="https://www.law-dictionary.org/"
                          rend="Internet%20link"
                          style="color: #0563c1; ">
                        <seg rend="Internet%20link" style="color: #0563c1; ">https://www.law-dictionary.org</seg>
                     </ref>)] or ten <seg style="">head of small cattle, for every square mile of the country so applied for'. Other clauses regulated rental terms, forfeiture and the like (</seg>'Northern territory pastoral regulations',<seg style="font-size: 10pt; "> </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">South Australian Government Gazette</seg>
                     <seg style="">, 28 December 1876, pp. 2701-3.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">F. J. H. von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">by his agent F Krichauff</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Witness—</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">James Binnie</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">___________</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Telegram under clause 5, sent to Northern Territory, dated</seg> 30th Jany <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">187</seg>8</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Approved by Government Resident, </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">vide</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; "> Telegram dated <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="8"/>187</seg>8.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">___________</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Forwarded to Treasury for receipt of first year's Rent, viz.:— £</seg> 3 : 5 : –</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">[illegible initials]</seg>
               <seg style="font-size: 10pt; font-style: italic; "> </seg>pro<seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">. Surveyor-General.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">25/4 <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">18</seg>78.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">___________</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Received the above amount of £ </seg>3 :5/<seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">: </seg>–<seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; "> this</seg> 25th <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">day of </seg>Apl <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">18</seg>78.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">C.R.T.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">pro Treasurer.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg>______________</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>being the holder of a preferential right to a lease of Run No. <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>, do solemnly declare that the said Run has been stocked, and continues to be stocked to the extent required by clause 2 of the Regulations under "The Northern Territory Land Act, 1876."</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">(Signature) __________________</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Declared before me at <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/> this <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/> day of <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>, 18</seg>
               <seg>
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">(Signature) _______________</seg>
               <seg> </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">J.P</seg>
               <seg>.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">Nr. the Mouth of the Roper River</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; ">Image courtesy of the National Archives of Australia. </seg>78-01-30_image01.jpg </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In the original sketch the vertical lines are approximately 7 cm (slightly less than 3 in) long. Given the dimensions marked on it, the sketch therefore does not conform to the instruction concerning the scale to be used.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">SCALE:— Four miles to one inch</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">accept the above diagram as</seg> my <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">act and deed.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">F. J. H. von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>by his agent F Krichauff </p>
         </div>
      </body>
